                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 MPC/9b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-09-28T23:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 28, 1943—11 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5974. The President has appointed Mr. Edwin C. Wilson, presently Ambassador to
                    Panama, as the representative of this Government on the Mediterranean
                    Commission.</p>
                <p>Please inform the appropriate authorities.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Berle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
